<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>We have been attempting to contact you regarding the outstanding payment for your Kingsbridge business insurance policy&nbsp;<b>[policy number]</b>.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b><br>Your policy is now at risk of cancellation.</b>&nbsp;If your insurance policy is cancelled,&nbsp;<u>your business may not be covered against claims if you don't have another insurance policy in place</u>.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u style=""><br><b>If a payment has not been made before&nbsp;</b><i style="font-weight: bold;">[proposed cancellation date]</i><b>, your policy will be cancelled from inception.<br></b></u></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u><b><br></b>Please be aware, if the policy is cancelled from inception, you will not be able to make a claim under it as it will be considered null and void.<br></u></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>To help you stay protected, please call us on&nbsp;<b>01242 808740</b>&nbsp;to make a payment or discuss further.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><u><br>Please note, for data security reasons, do not send credit or debit card details to us via email.<br></u></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><i><br>If you have made a payment in the past 3 working days please disregard this email.<br></i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>